# Branding

Event: Sitecore Silver, Tivoli Copenhagen, June 11 2026.

- **Colors**: silver `#b8b8b8` (400), dark `#1a1a1a`, gold `#d4af37` accents.
- **Theme**: dark-first; white/silver text on dark backgrounds.
- **Buttons**: `bg-gradient-to-br from-silver-500 to-silver-600`, hover scale/shadow.
- **Typography**: system stack; H1 large with silver gradient `bg-clip-text`.
- **Kiosk**: large touch targets, `md:`/`lg:` responsive grids.
- Full spec: `docs/BRANDING_GUIDE.md`, `tailwind.config.ts`, `src/app/globals.css`.
